*PagerPanel: (25x20, Id desk1, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, ActiveColorset 2, Frame 0)
*PagerPanel: (25x20, Id desk2, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 2, Frame 0)
*PagerPanel: (25x20, Id desk3, Title "4", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 2, Frame 0)
*PagerPanel: (100x80, Swallow FvwmPager 'Module FvwmPager *', Frame 1)
*PagerPanel: (4x3, Swallow DateTime 'Module FvwmScript $[FVWM_USERDIR]/scripts/Kalende/Kalende', Frame 0)

Style FvwmTaskBar !Title, BorderWidth 1, HandleWidth 1, Sticky, CirculateSkip, WindowListSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom
Style TaskBarIcons !Title, !Borders, !Handles, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkip, StaysOnBottom, NeverFocus, Sticky

DestroyModuleConfig TaskBarIcons:*
*TaskBarIcons: NumManagers        1
*TaskBarIcons: Title              ""
*TaskBarIcons: Resolution         global
*TaskBarIcons: Font               "xft:Fira Sans:style=Regular:size=11:antialias=True"
*TaskBarIcons: ButtonGeometry     192x28
*TaskBarIcons: MaxButtonWidth     192
*TaskBarIcons: Format             "%c: %i"
# *TaskBarIcons: ManagerGeometry    0x1+0-0
*TaskBarIcons: ManagerGeometry    1x1
*TaskBarIcons: DrawIcons          False
*TaskBarIcons: UseWinList         True
*TaskBarIcons: DontShow           Conky, XClock
*TaskBarIcons: ReliefThickness    1
*TaskBarIcons: PlainButton        raisededge
*TaskBarIcons: IconButton         raisededge
*TaskBarIcons: FocusButton        raisededge
*TaskBarIcons: FocusAndSelectButton    raisededge
*TaskBarIcons: SelectButton            raisededge
#*TaskBarIcons: Background         #2B303B
#*TaskBarIcons: Foreground         #2B303B
*TaskBarIcons: Colorset                 5
*TaskBarIcons: PlainColorset            5
*TaskBarIcons: IconColorset             5
*TaskBarIcons: FocusColorset            6
*TaskBarIcons: FocusAndSelectColorset   6
*TaskBarIcons: SelectColorset           4
*TaskBarIcons: IconAndSelectColorset    4
*TaskBarIcons: Shape                    true
*TaskBarIcons: Tips needed
*TaskBarIcons: TipsDelays 500 100
*TaskBarIcons: TipsColorset 14
*TaskBarIcons: TipsBorderWidth 1
*TaskBarIcons: TipsPlacement updown
*TaskBarIcons: TipsJustification left
*TaskBarIcons: TipsOffsets 2 4
*TaskBarIcons: TipsFont "xft:ubuntu:style=light:size=11:antialias=true"
*TaskBarIcons: Sort id
*TaskBarIcons: Action Mouse 0 A ret
*TaskBarIcons: Action Mouse 1 A sendcommand IconManClick
*TaskBarIcons: Action Mouse 3 A sendcommand "Menu MenuIconOps"

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmTaskBar:*
*FvwmTaskBar: Geometry $[vp.width]x28+0-0
*FvwmTaskBar: Colorset 5
*FvwmTaskBar: Rows 1
*FvwmTaskBar: Columns 60
*FvwmTaskBar: Frame 1
*FvwmTaskBar: Font "xft:Fira Sans:Medium:size=11:antialias=True:hinhstyle=slight"
# *FvwmTaskBar: (2x1, Title "", Icon "$[FVWM_USERDIR]/icons/fvwm-small.png", Action `Exec jgmenu --config-file=/home/doug/.config/jgmenu/jgfvwmrc`)
*FvwmTaskBar: (2x1, Title "Fvwm", Icon "", Action `Exec jgmenu --config-file="$HOME/.config/jgmenu/jgfvwmrc"`)
*FvwmTaskBar: (45x1, Top, Swallow FvwmIconMan 'Module FvwmIconMan TaskBarIcons', Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (6x1, Swallow(NoClose,UseOld) stalonetray 'Exec exec stalonetray --config "$HOME/.stalonetrayrc"', Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (1x1, Id desk0, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 0, Colorset 6, ActiveColorset 4, Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (1x1, Id desk1, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, ActiveColorset 4, Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (1x1, Id desk2, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 4, Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (1x1, Id desk3, Title "4", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 4, Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (3x1, Swallow DateTime 'Module FvwmScript $[FVWM_USERDIR]/BarClock', Action (Mouse 3) `Exec exec yad --width 360 --posx -200 --posy -200 --class="fbox_cal" --title="Fbox_Calendar" --calendar --text ""`, Frame 1)

# tint2 panel
Style FvwmTintBar !Title, BorderWidth 1, HandleWidth 1, Sticky, CirculateSkip, WindowListSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmTintBar:*
*FvwmTintBar: Geometry $[vp.width]x30+0-0
*FvwmTintBar: Colorset 5
*FvwmTintBar: Rows 1
*FvwmTintBar: Columns 10
*FvwmTintBar: Frame 1
*FvwmTintBar: Font "xft:Fira Sans:Medium:size=11:antialias=True:hinhstyle=slight"
Test (x tint2) *FvwmTintBar: (10x1, Swallow(NoClose,UseOld) tint2 `Exec exec tint2 -c ~/.config/tint2/tint2fvwmrc`, Frame 0)

# pager and desktop id
SetEnv DeskWidth  180
SetEnv DeskHeight 120

Style PagerBlock !Title, BorderWidth 1, HandleWidth 1, Sticky, CirculateSkip, WindowListSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom

# FvwmButtons - PagerBlock
#
# FvwmButtons is a powerful module that can be used to build custom
# panels and docks. This config uses FvwmButtons to build the PagerBlock.
# The panel contains buttons to switch desks, FvwmPager
#
DestroyModuleConfig PagerBlock:*
*PagerBlock: Geometry $[DeskWidth]x$[DeskHeight]-8+4
*PagerBlock: Colorset 23
*PagerBlock: Rows $[DeskHeight]
*PagerBlock: Columns 36
*PagerBlock: Frame 0
*PagerBlock: Font "xft:Sans:Bold:size=10:antialias=True"
*PagerBlock: (9x20, Id desk0, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 0, Colorset 22, ActiveColorset 23, Frame 1)
*PagerBlock: (9x20, Id desk1, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, ActiveColorset 23, Frame 1)
*PagerBlock: (9x20, Id desk2, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 23, Frame 1)
*PagerBlock: (9x20, Id desk3, Title "4", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 23, Frame 1)
*PagerBlock: (36x100, Swallow FvwmPager 'Module FvwmPager *', Frame 0)

Style DeskTopId !Title, !Borders, !Handles, Sticky, CirculateSkip, WindowListSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom

DestroyModuleConfig DeskTopId:*
*DeskTopId: Geometry 120x30-4+4
*DeskTopId: Colorset 23
*DeskTopId: Rows 1
*DeskTopId: Columns 4
*DeskTopId: Frame 1
*DeskTopId: Font "xft:Fira Code:style=Regular:size=11:antialias=true:hintstyle=slight"
*DeskTopId: (1x1, Id desk0, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 0, Colorset 22, ActiveColorset 23, Frame 0)
*DeskTopId: (1x1, Id desk1, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, ActiveColorset 23, Frame 0)
*DeskTopId: (1x1, Id desk2, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 23, Frame 0)
*DeskTopId: (1x1, Id desk3, Title "4", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 23, Frame 0)

Style TaskPanel !Title, BorderWidth 1, HandleWidth 1, Sticky, CirculateSkip, WindowListSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom

DestroyModuleConfig TaskPanel:*
*TaskPanel: Geometry $[vp.width]x28+0-0
*TaskPanel: Colorset 5
*TaskPanel: Rows 1
*TaskPanel: Columns 20
*TaskPanel: Frame 1
*TaskPanel: Font "xft:Fira Sans:Medium:size=11:antialias=True:hinhstyle=slight"
# *TaskPanel: (2x1, Title "", Icon "$[FVWM_USERDIR]/icons/fvwm-small.png", Action `Exec jgmenu --config-file=/home/doug/.config/jgmenu/jgfvwmrc`)
*TaskPanel: (1x1, Title "Fvwm", Icon "", Action `Exec jgmenu --config-file="$HOME/.config/jgmenu/jgfvwmrc"`)
*TaskPanel: (16x1, Top, Swallow FvwmIconMan 'Module FvwmIconMan TaskBarIcons', Frame 0)
*TaskPanel: (2x1, Swallow(NoClose,UseOld) stalonetray 'Exec exec stalonetray --config "$HOME/.stalonetrayrc"', Frame 0)
*TaskPanel: (1x1, Swallow DateTime 'Module FvwmScript $[FVWM_USERDIR]/BarClock', Action Mouse 3 A `Exec yad --width 360 --class="fbox_cal" --title="Fbox_Calendar" --calendar --text ""`, Frame 1)
